ween attacks.']\n['MOVING BETWEEN ATTACKS', 'How far can a fighter with a speed of 25 feet and the Multiattack feature move between attacks?', 'They can move 10 feet, make an attack, move 15 feet, and then attack a different target.']\n['USING DIFFERENT SPEEDS', 'Can you switch between different speeds during your move?', 'Yes, you can switch between different speeds during your move.']\n['USING DIFFERENT SPEEDS', 'How do you determine how much farther you can move when switching speeds?', \"Subtract the distance you've already moved from the new speed.\"]\n['DIFFICULT TERRAIN', 'How much extra movement does it cost to move through difficult terrain?', 'It costs 1 extra foot of movement for every foot of movement in difficult terrain.']\n['DIFFICULT TERRAIN', 'What are some examples of difficult terrain?', 'Low furniture, rubble, undergrowth, steep stairs, snow, shallow bogs, and the space of another creature.']\n['BEING PRONE', 'How much movement does it cost to stand up from prone?', 'It costs an amount of movement equal to half your speed to stand up from prone.']\n['BEING PRONE', 'How much extra movement does it cost to move while prone?', 'It costs 1 extra foot of movement for every foot of movement while prone.']\n['MOVING AROUND OTHER CREATURES', \"Can you move through a nonhostile creature's space?\", \"Yes, you can move through a nonhostile creature's space.\"]\n['MOVING AROUND OTHER CREATURES', \"Can you move through a hostile creature's space?\", \"You can only move through a hostile creature's space if the creature is at least two sizes larger or smaller than you.\"]\n['MOVING AROUND OTHER CREATURES', \"What happens if you leave a hostile creature's reach during your move?\", \"You provoke an opportunity attack if you leave a hostile creature's reach during your move.\"]\n['FLYING MOVEMENT', 'What happens if a flying creature is knocked prone, has its speed reduced to 0, or is otherwise deprived of the ability to move?', 'The creature falls unless it has